snippet.title: ITV News
snippet.description:
ITV News has been providing trusted and impartial news for more than 60 years. On our YouTube channel you'll find the best of our journalism from the UK and around the world. 

Subscribe to stay up-to-date with reports on the top news stories, explainers and analysis from our team of specialist correspondents to help you make sense of what’s happening, and must-see interviews and pictures.
